tems 95. Your customer wants to add the company’s email banner to each customer Facing email notification. how would you approach this requirement? a) create a company HTTP email wrapper b) create a company email template c) create a company CSS package for emails d) create a company email header and footer 96. what catalog tool would you use to create a catalog item or record',19,15,'43737c3e-ffdd-4542-901a-8e72b88a5a4c','2026-05-15 08:47:17','CSA');
