INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(235,1,235,'What does Order guide refer to in Service Catalog? Ans: Bundled Request (An order guide gives customers an easy way to order multiple related items as a single Where can you view information about system activity? system logs If the system is going to be upgraded,what will be exempt from the upgrade? Any record that has been altered from the base state by the customer How do you limit file attachments? Security>System Security SLAs include actions that can be triggered when during the lifecycle? Anytime What is a tool that will autopopulate the CMDB about your windows computer? Help the helpdesk What is A BSM Map? Business Service Management BSM map graphically displays the configuration items, CI, that support a business service. How are users related to roles or groups? 1 to Many Relation Where do you go in ServiceNow to change the banner and colors? System Properties, then CSS Properties What is the sequencing of publishing a Knowledge Article? Draft Review Publish service catalog workflow can be attached in 3 ways: manually on the catalog item form automatically based on conditions automatically if no other workflows attached How KB are organized? –By Topics and Categories KB articles are referred in which modules below (Service Catalog, News, INC)? Ans: News Role assignment. Ans: Inherits to group members if User customizes the Homepage, what happens? Ans: A prefix My is added to the homepage. 38.What is there stored in CMDB? Ans: Measurable tangible and intangible data of a CI. How ACL will execute? Ans: generic to specific What is the true if we delete the system table? Ans: Automatically recreated deleted System table in Next Upgrade When High Security plugin is activated? Ans: Penetration testing Out of the below listed applications which will not run natively on smartphones?',')Matrix Module b)Statistics Module c)Context menu d)View/Run Module What is the recommendation from service now for update set: Ans:Do not use Default update set All the applications of service which runs in browser will run in mobile. Ans:a)True b)Flase Changes made to gear will be applied to all the users. Ans:a)True b)False How many working SLAs can be attached to an Incident? Ans:a)More than 3 b)1 c)Infinite d)Less than 10 What is the important factor to remember when a user is creating cata',0,0,'2026-05-15 08:45:46.297009',1,'2026-05-15 08:45:46');
