INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(732,1,732,'A user reports that their newly provisioned server is not being populated in the CMDB, despite the CI being created successfully through the ServiceNow ITSM module. What would be the most likely cause of this issue, given that the CMDB data source is properly configured and the necessary credentials are in place?','Correct Answer: The CI''s discovery source is not set to populate the CMDB
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(733,1,733,'You need to configure a new CMDB data source to synchronize CI data from an external discovery tool. The tool provides a REST API for accessing CI data, but it requires authentication using a client certificate. What would be the best approach to authenticate the ServiceNow instance with the external tool?','Correct Answer: Use a MID Server with a configured client certificate to authenticate with the external tool
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(734,1,734,'A company has multiple business units, each with their own set of CI classes and discovery sources. The company wants to implement a centralized CMDB to provide a single, unified view of all CIs across the organization. What would be the best approach to organizing the CMDB data to support this requirement?','Correct Answer: Use a single CMDB table with a ''business_unit'' field to categorize CIs by business unit
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(735,1,735,'You are a ServiceNow CSA working on a project to implement CMDB for a large IT organization. The client wants to know the benefits of having an accurate and up-to-date CMDB. Which of the following benefits would you highlight as the most critical to the IT team?','Correct Answer: Facilitate impact analysis of proposed changes to reduce or eliminate downtime
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(736,1,736,'A user reports that they are having trouble navigating the CMDB in ServiceNow. They want to toggle between the CI Health Dashboard view and the form view. Where would you instruct them to find this option?','Correct Answer: In the form title bar
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(737,1,737,'You are working on a project to implement CSDM in ServiceNow. The client wants to know what CSDM is and how it will benefit their organization. Which of the following is a correct description of CSDM?','Correct Answer: Standard terms and definitions, Best Practice for CMDB Data Modeling and Data Management, and out of the box CMDB core tables
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(738,1,738,'A user reports that the CMDB is not accurately reflecting the relationships between Configuration Items (CIs), and as a result, service maps are not being generated correctly. To troubleshoot this issue, where would you navigate to review or create new Suggested Relationships?','Correct Answer: ALL > Configuration > Relationships > Suggested Relationships
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(739,1,739,'Your organization is implementing ServiceNow Service Mapping to overlay service maps onto existing configuration data. What approach does ServiceNow Service Mapping use to connect CIs underlying a given service, making the CMDB service aware?','Correct Answer: Top-down approach
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(740,1,740,'As a ServiceNow administrator, you are tasked with identifying and documenting the different types of Configuration Items (CIs) in your organization''s CMDB. Which of the following are examples of CIs that you would expect to find in the CMDB?','Correct Answer: Tangible entities, such as hardware and software, and Intangible entities, such as business services and email, and Configuration Item
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(741,1,741,'A large financial services organization is implementing ServiceNow CMDB to improve their IT service management. They have a complex infrastructure with multiple data centers, cloud services, and thousands of configuration items. What is the primary benefit of using the Common Service Data Model (CSDM) in this implementation?','Correct Answer: It enables true service level reporting and provides prescriptive guidance on service modeling within the CMDB
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(742,1,742,'You are a ServiceNow administrator tasked with optimizing the CMDB for a manufacturing company. The company has recently upgraded their ERP system and deployed new IoT devices on the shop floor. What type of tests should you run to ensure that the CMDB still works correctly after these changes?','Correct Answer: Quick start tests to verify CMDB functionality
INSERT INTO "flashcards" VALUES(743,1,743,'A user reports that they are unable to view the dependency view map for a specific configuration item in the CMDB. As a ServiceNow administrator, where would you navigate to troubleshoot this issue?','Correct Answer: Dependency Views > View Map
